## KEY INSIGHTS FROM COMPETITOR GAPS

**MAJOR OPPORTUNITY:** NO comprehensive editorial shopping guides exist - only brand pages and Pinterest boards. Create the definitive checklist with:
- Clear skill level organization (beginner/intermediate/advanced)
- Honest "must have vs nice to have" tags on every item
- Budget breakdowns showing total cost per level
- Kit vs individual cost comparison with real math
- Platform shopping guidance (where to buy each category)
- Organization tips BEFORE they buy (prevent storage overwhelm)

**Content Angle:** Position as "The Only Valentine Nail Supply List You Need" - comprehensive enough to be authoritative, organized enough to prevent overwhelm. Save readers from buying mistakes through honest "you don't need this yet" guidance.

**Conversion Strategy:**
- Skill level sections = users shop only their tier (targeted affiliate links)
- "Build Your Kit" bundle suggestions = higher cart value
- Comparison: $80 beginner kit vs $120 pre-made kit showing savings
- "Add to cart" quick lists at end of each section
- Storage/organization = Amazon basics organizers (additional commissions)

