## CRITICAL NOTES

- MUST include budget totals for each skill level (beginner: $80-110, intermediate: +$115-175, advanced: +$195-320)
- Kit vs individual comparison is CRITICAL - show real math proving individual is better value
- Tag every product: ESSENTIAL / RECOMMENDED / NICE-TO-HAVE / ADVANCED ONLY
